&lt;p&gt;
	I&amp;#39;m exited to announce the alpha2 release, to include bug fix and support for multiple ivr&amp;#39;s per application. Features included at this point by Astive Toolkit are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Multiple ivr&amp;#39;s per application.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Support for Asterisk 1.2 &amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Application-Server like operations(start, stop, undeploy, deploy...).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Control of multiple Asterisk servers at the same time.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		API&amp;#39;s for menu&amp;#39;s creation and Asterisk control.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Event-driven architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Well documented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
